snippet.title: Super Adventure Hand - Official Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for Super Adventure Hand to learn about the backstory involving awful feet, see gameplay, and more from this upcoming 3D platformer game. In Super Adventure Hand, you play as a hand on a gripping adventure where you single-handedly face numerous obstacles and avoid a handful of terrible feet. Super Adventure Hand is coming to PC, and a demo is available now on Steam.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
